{"word":"ἀναρπαστός","slug":"ἀναρπαστός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n7379\" key=\"a)narpasto/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀναρπ-αστός</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">όν</itype>, also <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ή</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">όν</itype> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg007.perseus-grc1:207\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hec.\">Hec.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">207</biblScope> </bibl> &lt;*&gt;lyr. &lt;*&gt;:—<sense id=\"n7379.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">snatched up, carried off,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀ. γίγνεσθαι</foreign> to be <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">carried off,</tr_> l. c., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg012:229c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phdr.\">Phdr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">229c</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n7379.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">carried up the country,</tr_> i. e. into Central Asia, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀ. γίγνεσθαι πρὸς βασιλέα</foreign> <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> l. in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:2:33\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mem.\">Mem.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.2.33</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n7379.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of things, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀ. ποιεῖν τὸν βίον</foreign> to give up his substance <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">as plunder,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:26:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.26.7</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0015.tlg001:7:3:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdn.\">Hdn.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.3.3</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}